Package: Yeskit
Type: Package
Title: Yet Another Single-Cell Analysis Toolkit (Yeskit)
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Wei Zhang
Maintainer: Wei Zhang <admin@ncrna.net>
Description: This is a single-cell analysis tookit. It can be used for single-cell gene expression matrices importation, 
    data integration, differential analysis, functional analysis, and visualization. It obeys the default data structure 
    of Seurat, and stores pathogen expression data and pathway enrichment scores in the obj@metadata slot and stores 
    differential gene analysis results and GO enrichment results in the obj@misc slot. Besides, Yeskit has the option to 
    rasterize the geom_point layer of ggplot2, while keep all axes, labels, and text in vector format.
